Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Namaste! I'm Sonia Goyal. I welcome you in my kitchen. Today, I'm preparing Rajasthani Gatta Pulao.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:42.000
Gatta Pulao will prepare in three steps. In first step, we will prepare Rajasthani Gatta with Gram flour. In second step, we will prepare rice. And, in third step, our Gatta Pulao will prepare.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:53.000
We need Gram flour, Salt, Red chili powder, Garam masala, edible oil and water to prepare Gatta.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:01.000
First of all, we will mix all the spices and edible oil in Gram flour.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:37.000
Then, we will make dough from this mixture by adding water in required quantity.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:13.000
Now, we will make its rolls and keep aside.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:49.000
Now, we boil some water in a pan, and put our gram flour rolls in this boiling water, and let these rolls boil for 15 minutes on medium flame with covered lid.

00:02:55.000 --> 00:03:03.000
After 15 minutes, we will take out these rolls and cut in 1/2 inch thick pieces.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.000
Now, we will cook rice.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:33.000
We need Basmati rice, Cumin seeds, Fresh green chili, Turmeric powder, Salt, Cumin seeds powder, Cloves, Black pepper whole, Black cardamom and edible oil.

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:41.000
First of all, we will boil rice in a pan with salt and turmeric powder.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:01.000
Then we will heat one tea spoon oil in a pan.

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:07.000
Add all the spices in it.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:25.000
We also add Rajasthani Gatta pieces in it and stir fry for 3-4 minutes.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:54.000
Finally, we add boiled rice in these spices. Mix the rice gently. Take away this Pulao from flame, and keep it covered for few minutes so that our Pulao will absorb the aroma of the spices.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:07.000
OUr delicious Rajasthani Gatta Pulao is ready.

